content:
Dulios was a Commander in the Naboo Royal Space Fighter Corps during the time of the Galactic Civil War. In 1 ABY, he was based in Theed Royal Palace, from where he sent a spacer to perform a number of tasks.
Dulios appeared as a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
